ğŸ”¹ Testing Approach
We followed the TDD (Test-Driven Development) methodology:
1.	Write a failing test for the feature.
2.	Implement the minimum code required to make the test pass.
3.	Refactor the code while keeping tests green.
Tools & Libraries
â€¢	Jest â†’ Unit Testing
â€¢	React Testing Library â†’ Component Testing
